Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've been able to relax like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you hit on me?!{唯をYuiナンパflirt, hit onしてよPlease}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd go anywhere if I could be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we walk{go out} together if we're living together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we hold hands, go to the movies, or eat lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Yui! Can't you see you're bothering him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm going to say what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind if you saw everything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've been holding in my feelings for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if everyone talks about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be scared if we're together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, should I leave this house and live on my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we'd just be classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you idiot!
