Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a fight with Ryuunosuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I got angry by myself... and cried by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like old times, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you fought with him,\N you'd come over to my bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for showing up so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd also want to speak up and tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm no longer a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want him to look at me only through pictures.{TLC?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts me to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could live by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine living without seeing his face every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That tickles, Yui-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of what Misako-san said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even if we don't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,children still grow up by themselves."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're becoming more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, stop teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On New Year's Day, I had a big fight with Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, Senpai's love affair was at a turning point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai will be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't worn this kind of clothing for a while, so it makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Sanshirou-san to see a different side of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good, Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wear a miniskirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to wear cute underwear that you won't mind being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This might be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually, I think pink suits you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been waiting long?{Miyuki's kinda asking really formally, I don't know why?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's because of the cold weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault for making you wait so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel warmer now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshirou-san, let's take a stroll and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I love taking walks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shoelace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at tying bow knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there were a sculptor and a critic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The sculptor believed in his talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He spent long hours perfecting his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of his criticism, the critic kept on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,studying sculpture day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There! That{bow knot} won't come loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of which of them is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be a sculptor who believes in himself and does his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A sculptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. All these words are actually from {googled, was female, don't know if married}Katagiri-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the best critic can't know the true essence of sculpture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I was supposed to meet Izumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The man... who assaulted me in the park... the other day... was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,someone I dated before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born into a strict family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I admired guys like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like hooligans, they're good at fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're kind to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, I considered him to be the ideal boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But he ignored my feelings, and that confused me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I began to think that his habitual kindness was just a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you asked me that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you kind to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A one-piece makes you look like you have no waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I don't want her to involve me in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for accompanying me despite my selfish demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When summer comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be able to swim in the real sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Katagiri-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be the protagonist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to have courage and the ability to take action.{ep1 0:16:04.68}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be a sculptor who believes in himself and does his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yousuke-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yousuke, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yousuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still wearing kids' underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you be better off\N if I taught you a few things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You! Don't be rude to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshirou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Losers shouldn't try protecting women in order to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!{lit: Raise your head!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't lay a hand on Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't want her to get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you. Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yousuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get up now. They've gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to apologize for, Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really bad at fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's the only tactic I could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what you said true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worthy to love anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, she's in the same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But as soon as she was accepted, she fell sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, will she be our kouhai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Aren't you going to take a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't gotten used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The nurses took care of her when she was hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels uncomfortable on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me, Sakurako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a shower together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a school swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hospitalized a lot, so I don't have any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Narusawa-senpai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You live with Ryuunosuke-senpai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she's Tsuzuki Kozue, a first-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently Ryuunosuke-kun is very popular.{Katagiri is saying that Ryuunosuke is not picky about girls "he's defence range is wide"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always dreamed of going to school in this uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then your dream will soon come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want another dream of mine to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's very short, isn't it?\N You have to be careful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never given it much thought, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some girls wear bloomers or spats underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It bothers me a bit when some old lecher looks at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I can't escort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I can go back by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to hurry. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you need help or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be waiting for someone{thing}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same. That's how I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting isn't good enough, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt different when I was with Yousuke-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is still beating hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget this night for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I wish I could make myself small.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'd fit inside your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We could be together whenever we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a dream, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:15:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll go to school tomorrow and clean Onii-chan's desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me if you want to turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to ask me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you don't want to be asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hurt Sanshirou-san's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please feel me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my heart beating wildly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because something very good happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This throbbing happens once in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you get to feel this way as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he'll like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he'll think I'm targeting him by wearing a matching set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late, Tomomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I did, but I'll forget about it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm poorly built?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And my lingerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think it looks cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At the hot springs, you helped me find my courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I've decided to face him squarely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing this "Lucky{Challenge} Underwear."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky Underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi-kun is over her troubles, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In contrast, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You look unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to give up just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You definitely didn't look cool back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not for you to decide whether you're worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my last magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of this temp job as a way of diverting yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting at 7 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your piano playing was different from your usual style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was intense but warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, your appearance is different too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your scent is different. I see! It's Yui-chan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
