Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I didn't bring anything here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think your purpose was to look at naked women, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No. I don't even know myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshirou-san—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd slept with\N Yousuke-kun at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But your attitude shows that\N you're completely inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That took the wind out of my sails.{拍子抜けしちゃった idiom}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go back if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath suddenly ran out of water.{I don't know if water run out, or boiler broke or what ever she just says broke}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was fine this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't finish talking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really persistent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that there's nothing left to say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other places, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, does it bother you if I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard what you said to Yousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you want to be my lover,\N you'd better look only at me.{this is a quote. May want to italic this}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't force me to follow in your footsteps."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to consider Yousuke to be the bad guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but did you even try?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you even try to understand him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wanting to be in love is like playing house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Any man who dates you will end up getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said this because\N I pity that kneeling guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not get close to Yousuke anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl like you would even bother the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, but it can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said about me and Yousuke-san might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,my relationship with\N Sanshirou-san is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot? That has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that's {\i1}your{\i0\fscx130} {\r}problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sanshirou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki... -san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshirou-san, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My breasts aren't very big.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a bit fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm trying my best to lose weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My biggest worry is my wide hips.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonetheless, this is the real me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to know more about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to repay you with my real self, for the courage you showed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know you better, and I want to fall for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I might've been kind to you just because I wanted you to look my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be sure if I can be kind to someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I know you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope things go well for Senpai and Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.25,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a god who supports people in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen you remove your ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My wish came true, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have beautiful hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd probably be jealous of anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I love told me there's someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty bad at giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.37,0:24:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,B-By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai asked me a very strange question.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.56,0:24:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me, "What is Lucky Underwear?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.42,0:24:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean by that?{That's silly.}
