Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.67,0:25:36.80,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}in front of the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.05,0:25:42.81,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I indecisively kept changing my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.81,0:25:48.73,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I made you wait half an hour longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.82,0:25:53.61,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Usually we joke around,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.24,0:25:58.58,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}but just holding hands and walking together
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.58,0:26:01.70,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.70,0:26:04.41,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Still, it was embarrassing too,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.41,0:26:12.63,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}so I couldn't look at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.09,0:26:16.89,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.01,0:26:23.39,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}this moment would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.39,0:26:28.90,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish we could watch the blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.90,0:26:34.40,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}just like this, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.69,0:26:38.49,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.49,0:26:44.54,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}my overflowing feelings would reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.95,0:26:50.50,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd just like to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:58.34,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}that I love you so much.
